en_158331_0	A police constable and a sergeant attached to Dodamgoda police were suspended in connection to brutally assaulting a motorcyclist at Dodamgoda Junction in Kalutara.
en_158331_1	Recently, footage of the two police officers assaulting a motorcyclist who did not have a driving license and disobeyed orders to stop the motorcycle was released by media.
en_158331_2	The police officers were suspended after investigating into the incident.
en_158331_3	The youth who was assaulted is currently receiving treatment at Nagoda Hospital in Kalutara.
